HEADWORD: Discoverable
<hw>Dis*cov"er*a*ble</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Capable of being discovered, found out, or perceived; <as>as, many minute animals are <ex>discoverable</ex> only by the help of the microscope; truths <ex>discoverable</ex> by human industry.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

